snippet.title: Cosmic Soundwaves
snippet.description:
Cosmic Soundwaves is a sanctuary of ambient music, cosmic soundscapes, tranquil meditation music and ancestral beats, dedicated to those seeking an oasis of beautiful sounds.
Hear Dave Bessell & Ishq, Holeg Spies, Lauge, Cold Womb Descent, Samo Zoko and other luminaries of the downtempo universe. 

Follow Chill Space Network on YouTube: 
► Chill Space 
http://bit.ly/ChillSpaceTV
